    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
  <div style="
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  ">

    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333;">
      Hello <strong><%= fullName %></strong>,
    </p>

    <p style="
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.6;
    ">
      Thank you for registering for
      <strong style="color: #4a6cf7;"><%= event %></strong>
      at <strong>Chakravyuh 2.0</strong>.
    </p>

    <!-- Registration Details -->
    <div style="
      background-color: #f9fafc;
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #e1e4ea;
      margin: 22px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    ">
      <h3 style="
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding-bottom: 6px;
      ">
        ðŸ“„ Registration Details
      </h3>

      <p style="margin: 6px 0; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>Registration ID:</strong> <%= registrationId %>
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 6px 0; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>Event:</strong> <%= event %>
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 6px 0; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>Date:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Payment Guidelines -->
    <% if (paymentRequired) { %>
    <div style="
      background-color: #fff8f2;
      border: 1px solid #ffd6b3;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 25px;
    ">
      <h3 style="
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #d35400;
      ">
        ðŸ’¡ Payment Guidelines
      </h3>

      <ul style="
        padding-left: 18px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.6;
      ">
        <li>Please complete the payment using the official payment link shared on the website or WhatsApp.</li>
        <li>Ensure that you enter the correct <strong>Registration ID</strong> during payment.</li>
        <li>Do not refresh or close the payment page until the transaction is completed.</li>
        <li>In case of payment failure, wait for a few minutes before retrying with <strong>new email address</strong>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Effectiveness Section -->
    <div style="
      background-color: #f2f7ff;
      border: 1px solid #d6e4ff;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    ">
      <h3 style="
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #2f5bd5;
      ">
        ðŸš€ Why Following These Guidelines Matters
      </h3>

      <p style="
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      ">
        Following the above payment guidelines helps us verify your transaction quickly,
        avoid delays in confirmation, and ensure your participation in Chakravyuh 2.0
        is processed smoothly and without errors.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p style="
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #b00020;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 18px;
    ">
      Your registration will be fully confirmed only after successful payment verification.
    </p>
    <% } %>

    <p style="
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #444;
      margin-top: 25px;
    ">
      If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at
      <a href="mailto:chakravyuh@sveri.ac.in" style="color: #4a6cf7; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
        chakravyuh@sveri.ac.in
      </a>
      or call us at
      <a href="tel:8669233747" style="color: #4a6cf7; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
        8669233747
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #444;">
      Best regards,<br>
      <strong>Team Chakravyuh</strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div style="
    margin-top: 15px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #777;
  ">
    <p style="margin: 0;">
      Â© <%= year %> Chakravyuh 2.0. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
